==English==
===Adjective===
'''specific'''
# [[explicit]] or [[definite]]
# of, or relating to a [[species]]
# [[special]], [[distinctive]] or [[unique]]
# [[intend]]ed for, or [[apply]]ing to a [[particular]] thing
# being a [[remedy]] for a particular [[disease]]
# ([[immunology]]) being [[limit]]ed to a particular [[antibody]] or [[antigen]]

====Translations====
*Catalan: específic
*Finnish: [[tietty]] (1), [[spesifinen]] (1)

===Noun===
'''specific'''  (plural ''[[specifics]]'')
# a [[remedy]] for a particular [[disorder]]
# a [[distinguishing]] [[attribute]] or [[quality]]

